{"title":"小胖子的难题","time_limit":2000,"memory_limit":250,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-4807","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>    3月22的晚上，小胖子被llg嘲讽了一波。</p><p>    为了展示自己的实力，小胖子决定解决抢在llg面前做出llg正在写的一道题目：</p><p>    给定一个长度为n的正整数序列，给定正整数L，求出长度最短的连续序列，使它们的和大于等于L。</p><p>    小胖子懵逼了，这么“神”的题居然卡了llg那么久，他随手一甩，把题目交给了你。<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行输入N，L</p><p>接下来一行读入N个数字</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>序列最短为多长</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>10 20</p><p>2 8 5 1 10 5 9 9 3 5 </p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>目标序列：10 5 9 或 5 9 9 或 9 9 3</p><p><br></p><p>尽你所能的优化算法，正在写题的llg露出一个神秘的笑容：他偷偷告诉你，最shabi的算法可以得10分，而好一点的可以得30-50分，而他刚刚打的才得了70分。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}